          "context": "<!--\n## Section-Toast\n\n**Type:** component\n**Component:** Toast\n\n### Purpose\nTransient notifications anchored bottom-right (default/success/error) plus the top-of-canvas Stale-Viewer-Banner triggered when a sync completes mid-session.\n\n### Design notes\n- Toasts: 280 wide pill, dark fill ($color-text-primary), white text, radius 14, padding [12,16]. Status carried by an 8px dot — success uses $tag-success-ink, error uses $tag-danger-ink.\n- Banner: full-width across canvas top, lighter surface, 14 type, prominent CTA. Sync-complete dot uses $tag-success-ink.\n-->",
