                          "context": "<!--\n## EmptyState-Icon\n\n**Type:** placeholder\n**Variant:** default\n**Component:** EmptyStateIcon\n\n### Purpose\nVisual hook at the top of the card. Right now it is a plain icon-in-rounded-square: 56x56 frame, radius 12, fill #F6F8F9, with a centered lucide git-branch glyph at 24px (D53MsD).\n\n### Design notes\n- Sits as the first child of EmptyState-Card, before the headline.\n- The frame chrome (square + soft fill) is a bigger, lighter cousin of the 28px Login-Mark on Login-Card.\n\n### For AI agents\n- This is a placeholder. Two acceptable evolution paths:\n  1. Short-term swap: replace the lucide icon (D53MsD) with the Carbon equivalent. Same dimensions, same square frame — just a more product-feeling glyph.\n  2. Long-term swap: replace the entire EmptyState-Icon frame with something more interesting — an illustration, a small animation, or any other piece of visual delight that suits a first-run moment. The container does not have to stay 56x56 if the replacement wants room to breathe.\n- Pick one based on the current product polish bar — do not stack both. Either swap the icon or swap the whole thing.\n-->",
