          "id": "bn1uf",
          "name": "Dashboard-populated-wrap",
          "context": "<!--\n## Dashboard-populated-wrap\n\n**Type:** wrap\n**Variant:** layout container\n**Component:** Dashboard populated flow\n\n### Purpose\nWrapper around Dashboard-populated-final — the default landing surface for a signed-in user with at least one connected repo. One of the three landing-flow surfaces on this canvas (sisters: Dashboard-expanded-wrap, ConnectRepo-wrap).\n\n### For AI agents\n- Wrap is a canvas-only label shell — only ship the inner Dashboard-populated-final.\n- The inner page is built from two sections that repeat across the other wraps:\n  - Recent Repos (s4QqfU) — same primitive as Dashboard-expanded-wrap KNRCz and ConnectRepo-Step3 (R1zlTn).\n  - RepoList (PyuN0) — same primitive as Dashboard-expanded-wrap aHZOW and ConnectRepo-wrap connS2List.\n- Header (V9Tu3H) carries the FilterPills cluster on the right that is not present in the expanded variant — that is the only structural difference between the two dashboard layouts above the list.\n-->",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 12,
          "children": [
