        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "iorFn",
          "name": "Dashboard-expanded-wrap",
          "context": "<!--\n## Dashboard-expanded-wrap\n\n**Type:** wrap\n**Variant:** layout container\n**Component:** Dashboard expanded flow\n\n### Purpose\nWrapper around Dashboard-expanded-final. One of the three landing-flow surfaces on this canvas (sisters: Dashboard-populated-wrap, ConnectRepo-wrap).\n\n### For AI agents\n- Wrap is a canvas-only label shell — only ship the inner Dashboard-expanded-final.\n- Two cross-cutting patterns inside this wrap also appear in the populated wrap and the connect wrap:\n  - Recent Repos (KNRCz here, s4QqfU on populated, ConnectRepo-Step3 / R1zlTn on connect — all three are header bar + horizontal card grid in #f0f3f4 surface).\n  - RepoList (aHZOW here, PyuN0 on populated, connS2List on connect — all three are stacked rows in #f0f3f4 surface).\n- Worth promoting both to shared layout primitives.\n-->",
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 12,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "id": "BnAOT",
              "name": "expLabel",
              "fill": "#9b9295",
              "content": "04 / Dashboard — repo expanded + workspace popover",
              "lineHeight": 1,
              "fontFamily": "Geist",
              "fontSize": 12,
              "fontWeight": "500"
            },
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "iC6rE",
              "name": "Dashboard-expanded-final",
              "context": "<!--\n## Dashboard-expanded-final\n\n**Type:** layout\n**Variant:** expanded + popover-open\n**Component:** Dashboard\n\n### Purpose\nShows two interactions stacked on the populated dashboard at once: (a) one repo row expanded so its pinned branches are visible inline, and (b) a workspace popover open after clicking a team chip on a different row (build plan lines 158–172).\n\n### Design notes\n- Branch rows are 48px tall and indented 32px from row left to make the hierarchy obvious without nesting cards.\n- Pinned branches show a filled lucide `pin` icon (#121111). Unpinned would be ghost icon revealed on hover only.\n- 'Other branches…' expander lazy-loads from GitHub on click (build plan line 170).\n- WorkspacePopover-final is an anchored panel: 280 wide, white surface, 1px #E1E4E5, radius 12, soft shadow. It floats absolute-positioned above the row below the chip.\n- Branch row meta uses Geist Mono 12 #6d6467 for SHA + relative timestamp; status dot uses the same kit as RepoRow.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Sibling layouts: Dashboard-empty-final, Dashboard-populated-final.\n- Branch row component variants live in the kit (BranchRow-default-final, BranchRow-syncing-final, BranchRow-pinned-final, BranchRow-failed-final, BranchRow-stale-final).\n- WorkspacePopover-final lives in the kit; this layout instances it with the 'Acme' workspace.\n-->",
              "width": 1440,
              "height": 1080,
              "fill": "#ffffff",
              "cornerRadius": 16,
              "stroke": {
                "align": "inside",
                "thickness": 1,
                "fill": "#E1E4E5"
              },
              "layout": "vertical",
              "children": [
                {
                  "id": "CQMK6",
                  "type": "ref",
                  "ref": "bmFW0",
                  "name": "expTb",
                  "x": 0,
                  "y": 0
                },
                {
                  "type": "frame",
                  "id": "Lm1KZ",
