          "id": "R41htS",
          "name": "ConnectRepo-wrap",
          "context": "<!--\n## ConnectRepo-wrap\n\n**Type:** wrap\n**Variant:** layout container\n**Component:** ConnectRepo flow\n\n### Purpose\nTop-level wrapper for the /connect screen layout exhibit. One of the three landing-flow surfaces on this canvas (sisters: Dashboard-populated-wrap, Dashboard-expanded-wrap).\n\n### For AI agents\n- The wrap is a canvas-only label shell — only ship the inner ConnectRepo-default-final.\n- The two interactive sections inside (ConnectRepo-Step2 selecting a repo, ConnectRepo-Step3 picking a workspace) reuse visual primitives that also appear on the dashboard wraps. Treat the visual overlap as a hint, not a contract.\n-->",
