                              "name": "WorkspaceCard-team-selected",
                              "context": "<!--\n## WorkspaceCard-team-selected\n\n**Type:** state\n**Variant:** selected (radio active)\n**Component:** WorkspaceCard\n\n### Design notes\n- Selected state uses a soft top-down blue gradient (#ffffff at 0.4, #e7eefe at 0.8, #c0d2fc at 1.0) to lift the card without a heavy ring. 1.5px stroke instead of 1px reinforces selection.\n- Original inline note: the gradient is used here to highlight that this one is selected. Preserved so future agents see the original intent.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Pair with WorkspaceCard-personal-default. Together they form a radio group within ConnectRepo-Step3.\n- The gradient-as-highlight pattern is reused on Repo Card (kGxUt / mHl8h) inside Recent Repos but with a darker palette to read as most accessed. Treat both as instances of the same highlighted card visual language.\n-->",
