          "type": "frame",
          "id": "g4zm4h",
          "name": "Dashboard-empty-final",
          "context": "<!--\n## Dashboard-empty-final\n\n**Type:** layout\n**Variant:** empty\n**Component:** Dashboard\n\n### Purpose\nState shown at / when the signed-in user has no repo connections in any workspace they belong to. Pushes the user toward /connect.\n\n### Design notes\n- Page bg #f6f6f9, top bar (DashboardTopBar-final) is the only chrome.\n- EmptyState is centered vertically and horizontally below the top bar. Headline Geist 22/500 #121111. Body Geist 13 #6d6467, max width ~420.\n- Single primary action only (`+ Connect a repo`). No filter chips, no list affordances.\n- Workspace switcher in top bar still functions — the user can flip between joined workspaces to confirm they're all empty.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Sibling layouts: Dashboard-populated-final, Dashboard-expanded-final.\n- The EmptyState component is also used inside workspace popovers when a team has zero repos.\n- The Connect-Label override on the top bar can read 'Connect first repo' on this state if desired.\n-->",
          "clip": true,
          "width": 1440,
          "height": 900,
          "fill": "$color-bg-secondary",
          "cornerRadius": 16,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": 1,
            "fill": "$color-border-secondary"
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "epo6g",
              "layoutPosition": "absolute",
              "x": 0,
              "y": 0,
              "name": "emptyTb",
              "context": "<!--\n## DashboardTopBar-final\n\n**Type:** component\n**Variant:** default\n**Component:** DashboardTopBar\n\n### Purpose\nPersistent top bar across /, /connect, and /[workspace]/[repo]/[branch]. Provides workspace switching, global search, primary 'Connect new repo' action, and the user avatar.\n\n### Design notes\n- 64px tall, 1440 wide. White surface with #E1E4E5 bottom hairline only.\n- Workspace switcher mirrors Sidebar-Header (8zJLA): dark mono initial avatar, two-line meta, chevrons-up-down trigger.\n- Search input mirrors Sidebar-Search-Bar (XlkGy): 32px tall, 1px #E1E4E5 border, lucide search icon, mono placeholder for fuzzy repo lookups.\n- Primary action (#121111 fill, white label, radius 14) is `+ Connect new repo` per build plan line 132.\n- Avatar 32px, dark fill, mono initial.\n- Reusable so all dashboard layouts share the same bar.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Override `WorkspaceSwitcher-name` text via descendants to switch contexts.\n- Override `Connect-Label` for variants like 'Connect first repo' on the empty state.\n- The bar itself never changes structurally between layouts — only inner copy.\n-->",
              "width": 1440,
              "height": 64,
              "fill": "#ffffffff",
              "stroke": {
