      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "m8Uxu",
          "name": "asLabel",
          "fill": "#9b9295",
          "content": "06 / AppShell with new instance breadcrumb",
          "lineHeight": 1,
          "fontFamily": "Geist",
          "fontSize": 12,
          "fontWeight": "500"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "en05X",
          "name": "AppShell-with-breadcrumb-final",
          "context": "<!--\n## AppShell-with-breadcrumb-final\n\n**Type:** layout\n**Variant:** default + instance breadcrumb\n**Component:** AppShell\n\n### Purpose\nThe existing AppShell at /[workspace]/[repo]/[branch] with the new instance breadcrumb at the very top of the sidebar (build plan lines 174–176). Users can switch branches inline via the branch dropdown without returning to the dashboard.\n\n### Design notes\n- Two-column shell: 280 sidebar + canvas area, both 1px #dfe0e7, radius 16, white surface — matches existing Sidebar-Final-Demo (bMuHk) and PanelB-Enhanced-final (myB63) on the canvas.\n- InstanceBreadcrumb sits ABOVE the existing workspace switcher (Sidebar-Header) — this is the only structural change to the AppShell.\n- Breadcrumb separators use lucide chevron-right at #9b9295. Workspace + repo render in Geist Mono 12. Branch is a clickable trigger with caret-down (lucide chevron-down).\n- Variant InstanceBreadcrumb-branch-dropdown-open-final lives in the component kit; instancing it here would float a 240-wide menu anchored to the breadcrumb branch trigger.\n- Canvas area shows the existing PanelB-Enhanced-final preview — placeholder rectangle stands in for the live iframe.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Do NOT redesign the AppShell. Only the InstanceBreadcrumb is new; everything else mirrors the existing canvas nodes.\n- Branch dropdown component variants: collapsed (this layout) + open (kit).\n- The breadcrumb gives users a way to jump branches without the dashboard round-trip.\n-->",
          "clip": true,
          "width": 1440,
          "height": 900,
          "fill": "#f6f6f9ff",
          "cornerRadius": 16,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": 1,
            "fill": "#dfe0e7"
          },
          "gap": 16,
          "padding": 16,
