          "type": "frame",
          "id": "qvQ7F",
          "name": "RepoList",
          "context": "<!--\n## RepoList\n\n**Type:** section\n**Variant:** stacked rows (state showcase, no expansion)\n**Component:** RepoList / RowList\n\n### Purpose\nThe all-repos panel. Vertical list of 7 RepoRow children covering default, hover, syncing, stale, failed, and team-chip states — this wrap doubles as the canonical row-state showcase.\n\n### Design notes\n- Same surface primitive as aHZOW on Dashboard-expanded-wrap, ConnectRepo-Step3 / connS2List, and Recent Repos (#f0f3f4 / radius 18 / 2px padding / 1px stroke).\n\n### For AI agents\n- Same consolidation question as on aHZOW: a shared RowList container + Row base, with RepoRow / BranchRow / ConnectRepoRow as content variants.\n- When the row component lands in code, port these as the documented variants (default, hover, syncing, stale, failed, default+team-chip).\n-->",
          "clip": true,
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "#f0f3f4",
