        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "AJNcY",
          "name": "Section-WorkspaceChip-v2",
          "context": "<!--\n## Section-WorkspaceChip-v2\n\n**Type:** component\n**Component:** WorkspaceChip\n\n### Purpose\nInline ownership chip on every RepoRow indicating personal vs team. Click target opens WorkspacePopover (the popover lives only in the original kit).\n\n### Design notes (v2)\n- Pill shape: 28 tall, radius 8, padding [4,8] for dot variants and [4,10] for avatar variants.\n- Personal carries a 6px $color-text-tertiary dot + Geist 13 #6d6467 label.\n- Team carries an 18 dark mono initial avatar + Geist 13 #121111 label. The avatar reuses the same 28-mono-initial archetype as the TopBar workspace switcher.\n- Active state (popover open) gets a 1px $color-text-primary ring + #f6f8f9 fill.\n- Hover state gets only the #f6f8f9 fill — no ring, no underline.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Place this chip inside RepoRow's right cluster, just before the status dot.\n- Don't replace the avatar with a colored dot for team chips — the dark mono initial pattern is the brand-level workspace identity.\n-->",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "#ffffff",
          "cornerRadius": 16,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": 1,
            "fill": "#E1E4E5"
