        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "OvAbs",
          "name": "Section-BranchRow-v2",
          "context": "<!--\n## Section-BranchRow-v2\n\n**Type:** component\n**Component:** BranchRow\n\n### Purpose\nNested row revealed when a RepoRow expands. 48 tall, indented 32 from row left. Pin icon, status dot, mono branch name, last sync meta.\n\n### Design notes (v2)\n- Row pill: radius 16, fill #f6f8f9 (matches the expanded RepoRow background tint), padding [12,20,12,48] (32 indent), gap 12, height 48.\n- Left cluster: lucide pin icon (filled when pinned, ghost when unpinned) + 8px status dot + Geist Mono 13 #121111 branch name.\n- Right cluster: Geist Mono 12 #6d6467 SHA + Geist Mono 12 #6d6467 relative time. Hover reveals 'Open' ghost link in $color-text-primary.\n- Pinned branches auto-rebuild on push (build plan line 172).\n\n### For AI agents\n- BranchRow is always rendered inside an expanded RepoRow's row group, never on the dashboard surface alone. The matching #f6f8f9 fill is what visually attaches the branch to its parent repo.\n- Failed and stale states use the same dot semantics as RepoRow: $tag-danger-ink fill / $color-text-tertiary ring respectively.\n-->",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "fill": "#ffffff",
          "cornerRadius": 16,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": 1,
            "fill": "#E1E4E5"
