    {
      "type": "frame",
      "id": "ceYye",
      "x": 8518,
      "y": 5702,
      "name": "Section-InstanceBreadcrumb-v2",
      "context": "<!--\n## Section-InstanceBreadcrumb-v2\n\n**Type:** component\n**Component:** InstanceBreadcrumb\n\n### Purpose\nSits at the top of the AppShell sidebar inside `/[workspace]/[repo]/[branch]`. Shows the resolved instance and lets users switch branch without going back to the dashboard.\n\n### Design notes (v2)\n- Closed: inline trail with workspace mono initial (18 dark, radius 6) + workspace label, chevron-right separator, mono repo (truncatable), chevron-right, branch token (mono + chevron-down).\n- Branch token is the only interactive segment — opens a 240-wide menu beneath itself with the pinned branches first, then 'Other branches…' lazy expander, mirroring the dashboard's expanded RepoRow.\n- Hover state on branch token: #f6f8f9 fill, 1px #E1E4E5 ring.\n- Open state: branch token swaps chevron-down for chevron-up, the dropdown panel renders below with radius 12, soft shadow, 1px #E1E4E5.\n\n### For AI agents\n- Display these in a sidebar-width frame (≈280) with white fill so the trail reads at its intended scale.\n- Don't expose workspace switching from this trail — that's the TopBar's job. This trail switches branch only.\n-->",
      "width": "fill_container(784)",
      "fill": "#ffffff",
      "cornerRadius": 16,
      "stroke": {
        "align": "inside",
        "thickness": 1,
        "fill": "#E1E4E5"
      },
      "layout": "vertical",
      "gap": 16,
      "padding": 24,
      "children": [
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "TnjSi",
          "name": "InstanceBreadcrumb-Heading",
          "fill": "#121111",
          "content": "InstanceBreadcrumb",
          "lineHeight": 1.2,
          "fontFamily": "Geist",
          "fontSize": 16,
          "fontWeight": "500"
        },
        {
          "type": "text",
          "id": "PujHM",
          "name": "InstanceBreadcrumb-Desc",
          "fill": "#6d6467",
          "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "content": "Trail at the top of the AppShell sidebar inside /[workspace]/[repo]/[branch]. Branch token opens a dropdown for in-place switching.",
          "lineHeight": 1.4,
          "fontFamily": "Geist",
          "fontSize": 14,
          "fontWeight": "normal"
        },
        {
          "type": "frame",
          "id": "q3zPE1",
          "name": "InstanceBreadcrumb-Display",
          "width": "fill_container",
          "cornerRadius": 18,
          "stroke": {
            "align": "inside",
            "thickness": 1
          },
          "layout": "vertical",
          "gap": 24,
          "padding": 24,
          "children": [
            {
              "type": "frame",
              "id": "s8Qaa",
              "name": "IB-Container",
