          "context": "<!-- ## Nav-Search\n**Type:** input\n**Component:** DashboardNav-Search\n### Design notes\n- 480 wide × 36 tall, white pill radius 12, 1px #e8ebed border. Lucide `search` glyph (#9b9295) + Geist 14 placeholder + ⌘K kbd hint pill on the trailing edge.\n### For AI agents\n- Open the global command palette on cmd/ctrl+K. Wire to the existing CommandPalette primitive when one is added.\n- Override `Nav-Search-Placeholder` text via descendants for context-specific placeholders.\n-->",
