              "context": "<!-- ## Nav-Connect-Button\n**Type:** primary button\n**Component:** DashboardNav-Connect\n### Design notes\n- Dark (#171719) fill, white Ronzino 16 label, radius 12, height 36, padding [16,20].\n### For AI agents\n- When codifying, swap with the dark variant of the project's PrimaryButton system rather than reproducing this frame.\n- Override `Nav-Connect-Label` text via descendants for variants like 'Connect first repo' on the empty state.\n-->",
