              "type": "frame",
              "id": "HoiCg",
              "name": "Nav-Avatar",
              "context": "<!-- ## Nav-Avatar\n**Type:** avatar trigger\n**Component:** DashboardNav-Avatar\n### Design notes\n- 36×36 circle (radius 40), dark→cool-blue→cream linear gradient as the placeholder fill.\n### For AI agents\n- Bind to the shadcn Avatar primitive. The gradient fill here is the default state when no GitHub or Google profile image is available.\n- Clicking should open a user-controls popover (logout, settings, etc.) — popover not yet designed.\n-->",
              "width": 36,
              "height": 36,
              "fill": {
                "type": "gradient",
                "gradientType": "linear",
                "enabled": true,
                "rotation": -180,
